# Registration Form

A basic user registration form built using HTML and CSS to demonstrate form handling and input validation.

## 📌 Features

- Text, Email, Password, and Mobile input fields
- Required field validation
- Dropdown selection (Gender)
- Pattern validation for mobile numbers
- Basic CSS styling

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in any web browser.
2. Fill out the form fields to test validation.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- HTML form elements
- Input validation
- Required attributes
- Styling form components

